<hymn_number>170</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
.    Am                   Dm
 Terbetedi áýen meniń janymdy,
.E                 Am
 Tyńdaı ma eken Táńir meniń ánimdi?
.  Am                          Dm
 Qaıta-qaıta keldi júrekke osy án.
.     E7            Am
 Madaqtasam dep em Isa Táńirdi.

[V2]
 Júregimde ornap Seniń sózderiń,
 Ashyldy ǵoı Iem, meniń kózderim.
 Aq jolyńa tústim, basta Sen meni.
 Aıtqanyna ermen endi ózgeniń.

[V3]
 Aqıqatty nusqa, ashyp ulyńa,
 Oıanysh ber meniń alys qyryma.
 Madaqtaıyn Seni, Isa Táńirim.
 Aq batańdy bershi osy jyryma.

[V4]
 Kókte Seniń dańqyń arta bersinshi,
 Barlyq halqym kelip Saǵan ersinshi.
 Ashshy Óziń júregin qazaq elimniń,
 Adamzatqa dańqyń qaıta kelsinshi.

[V5]
 Madaqtańdar, dostar, Táńirdi búgin,
 Madaqtańdar osy ulylyǵy úshin.
 Aspanmenen jerde madaqtańdarshy,
 Iemizdiń raqym, shapaǵaty úshin.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<title>Terbetedi áýen meniń janymdy РӘЖ62</title>
</song>